Commentary Text: RS Hangargekar to Saha, out Caught by Shivam Dube!! Hangargekar strikes in his first over. Saha flashes away from his body against this length ball and the thick outside edge flies towards square third man. Dube sprints across to his right, keeps his eyes on the ball and completes a fantastic catch diving to his right. Saha is waiting on the sidelines to check out for the replays, but it's a clean catch. The opening partnership has been broken, so we can expect a few more wickets over the next few overs. Saha c Shivam Dube b RS Hangargekar 25(16) [4s-2 6s-2]
